<h1>Type Description</h1>
<p class="tips_img">ISTJ   Functional Preference Ordering:</p>

<p>
<U><B>Dominant:</B></U>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Introverted Sensing<br />
<U><B>Secondary:</B></U>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  Extraverted Thinking<br />
<U><B>Tertiary:</B></U> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Feeling<br />
<U><B>Inferior: </B></U>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Extraverted Intuition</p>
